Description: NEW WITH TAGS, CASE, AND MANUAL. Invicta 50mm Subaqua Noma III Swiss Made Quartz Chronograph Bracelet Watch A superior timekeeping authority, this Invicta Subaqua Noma III perfectly polishes your professional attire! Beginning with a round silver-tone stainless steel case and a unidirectional rotating bezel, this Subaqua exudes tradition and texture. The gold-tone bezel boasts Arabic numerals, three barrel accents and a fixed bezel with a diver’s scale and luminous markers. A three link bracelet concludes this Subaqua’s commanding appearance with knurl textured inner links. Crafted with care in its construction, a metal dial presents a 1/10th-seconds subdial near 2:00, a date window near 4:00, a 60-seconds subdial above 6:00, a 30-minute subdial at 9:00 and a tachymeter scale along the outer edge. Tritnite accents the index markers and hour, minute, subdial and chronograph hands while “Invicta” and its logo settle below 12:00. Elevate your style status with the excellence and expertise of this Invicta Subaqua Noma III!
